ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectCUFTA Rules of Origin Regulations
PrecisCUFTA RULES OF ORIGIN REGULATIONS in order to repeal and replace the current Regulations to allow materials of any non-Party with which both Canada and Ukraine have free trade agreements to be taken into consideration by the exporter when determining whether a product produced in Ukraine or Canada qualifies as originating under CUFTA.
